mg src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557f46161928e46acaf186abbca9d6c78be56a76","tid":422938,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"係呀  所以移民咗去紐西蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5140d96edd87d7b41099d80a771857c2ec3063e","tid":422938,"uid":148197,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T13:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暗瘡好多因素架<br />\n如果咁簡單就解決到就唔洗咁多人睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明，我都係過來人。 但我成日覺得如果自己都唔做好，真係冇人會幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab1055100467e6779c036e4a33f762a641cdddb","tid":422938,"uid":15880,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:13:38.000Z","msg":"DNA 冇事既每晚通頂 3餐M記都唔會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49b02bd6a41e394fb3a55b7c2a1290898b68c393","tid":422938,"uid":73848,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:43:42.000Z","msg":"唔洗聽樓主講，食A酸才是王道"},{"pid":"4dbb0f4e692beaec8eef35d942fa31a90c0c8239","tid":422938,"uid":144198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:48:20.000Z","msg":"有啲人生暗瘡未必關飲食同皮膚護理事 可能佢哋本身皮膚性質就係暗瘡肌/油肌令到佢哋容易啲出暗瘡 有啲人就係因為壓力導致暗瘡"},{"pid":"a17e71ff52d40d451b530d799af6d006e4ad90e4","tid":422938,"uid":75307,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:50:19.000Z","msg":"屌我一黎M生到成面都係<br />\n就算真係做哂你講果啲野都會照爛面"},{"pid":"9a9e1d3d109c5fdbc560ffd2b8bf46e9a5415073","tid":422938,"uid":18118,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:50:38.0